[h3 id=MainComments 
	" Main Comments
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Oddworld: Abe's Oddysee is a 2D side scrolling platform game released in 1997 for the PS1 and PC. In 2014, a TAS was made by Samtastic and Dooty which introduced a new skip in the Monsaic Lines which allows us to skip Paramonia and Scrabania. 4 years later, a new speedrunner came along from Spain and improved the bee DDG in the Monsaic Lines. Then, after looking into this glitch a bit more, Legna found a way on setting up the DDG on the bottom instead of the top. Then, on December 25th 2018, Legna out of nowhere discovered a faster way on setting up the DDG that is now faster than the previous movie. It also has a 20% success rate on getting it to work in an RTA run. The movie beats the current published movie by 3 seconds! The movie is 160 frames faster than the previous movie! 
	$LF
]p
