[h3 id=Improvements 
	" Improvements
	$LF
]h3
[h4 id=MonsaicLines 
	" Monsaic Lines
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"This section has made the frame difference thanks to Legna's new strat on setting up the DDG in the Monsaic Lines. We now no longer need to wait for Abe to get attacked by the bees by himself. Instead, at a random moment, the bees will automatically fly towards Abe and Abe can move to the bells whilst getting attacked. Abe needs to have 64 HP before he can trigger the DDG.
	$LF
]p
